Tlul '''Sakra''' g udewwar n Kunuha g uzmez n uhukagi wiss kraḍ, seg temẓi-nnes da tettiri Saski llig t-teẓra slawan akkʷ seg wussan n Takadimit, tgadda d Naṛutu d Saski g wawtay , tucka-d dit-sen g trabbut tiss sa, tenfel tudert-nnes llig iffeɣ Saski seg Kunuha, teg tanelmadt n uhukagi wiss semmus Tsunadi afad ad tessdus iɣef-nnes d ad d-trar Saski, tga tamsegnaft n trabbut tiss sa, ar bedda teswingim g Saski d da teskar uggar n ma mi teẓḍar afad ad t-trar s Kunuha meqqar da bedda tetteqqel s Naṛutu ad tt-illil g tassasin-nnes, tiwes bahra i tamunt n icinubiyen g umgaru wiss kkuẓ s uswuri-nnes g ussesfer n imagusen, tiwes awed g yimiɣ mgel Madara d Kaguya d Ubitu lli issnekren amgaru, tiwel sul g tgira s Saski taru(tarew) di-s Sarada lli igan seg tasut tamaynut n Naṛutu : Buṛutu .

